---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Voluntariado | AAEGB" description="Saiba como se voluntariar para os projetos da AAEGB e apoiar as comunidades locais.">
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-[#F7F5F0]">
    <section class="bg-forest-900 text-white py-24">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-saffron uppercase tracking-[0.35em] mb-4">Voluntariado</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">Junte-se ą aēćo em Cacine.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-lg">Seja voluntįrio e ajude a ampliar educaēćo, saśde e infraestrutura com trabalho, troca de saberes e parceria comunitįria.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
          <a href="/contato" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-saffron px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-forest-950 shadow-xl hover:opacity-95 transition">Quero ser voluntįrio</a>
          <a href="/projetos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white hover:bg-white/15 transition">Conhecer projetos</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20">
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-ember font-black mb-4">Missćo</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Apoiar aēões educacionais, de saśde e cultura junto ą comunidade de Cacine.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-ember font-black mb-4">Perfil</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Buscamos pessoas engajadas, sensķveis ao contexto local e dispostas a colaborar com responsabilidade.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-ember font-black mb-4">Como participar</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Envie uma mensagem para nossa equipe de voluntariado e receba orientaēões sobre as oportunidades atuais.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
